---

---

<section class="section section--surface">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="impact__grid">
      <div class="impact__image">
        <div class="impact__image-placeholder">
          <svg
            width="64"
            height="64"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="1.5"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            ><path
              d="M19 14c1.49-1.46 3-3.21 3-5.5A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 16.5 3c-1.76 0-3 .5-4.5 2-1.5-1.5-2.74-2-4.5-2A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 2 8.5c0 2.3 1.5 4.05 3 5.5l7 7Z"
            ></path></svg
          >
        </div>
        <div class="impact__image-overlay"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="impact__content">
        <h2 class="section-title">Impacto de tu Donación</h2>
        <p class="impact__text">
          Cada donación de sangre puede salvar hasta tres vidas. Tu generosidad
          no solo ayuda a pacientes en emergencias, sino que también apoya
          tratamientos contra el cáncer y cirugías complejas en todo el país.
        </p>
        <div class="impact__stats">
          <div class="impact__stat">
            <span class="impact__stat-value">3</span>
            <span class="impact__stat-label">Vidas Salvadas</span>
          </div>
          <div class="impact__stat">
            <span class="impact__stat-value">15m</span>
            <span class="impact__stat-label">Tiempo de Donación</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .impact__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .impact__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }

  .impact__image {
    position: relative;
    height: 400px;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fadbda 0%, #ffe1e0 50%, #f1d3d2 100%);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .impact__image-placeholder {
    color: #bc002d;
    opacity: 0.4;
  }

  .impact__image-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(188, 0, 45, 0.3), transparent);
  }

  .impact__content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .impact__text {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #5c403f;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .impact__stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .impact__stat {
    padding: 1rem;
    background-color: #fff0ef;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
  }

  .impact__stat-value {
    display: block;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #8f0020;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .impact__stat-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: #5c403f;
  }
</style>
